'''Fuhrländer Wind Turbine Laasow''' is a [[wind turbine]], built in 2006 near the village of [[Laasow]], [[Brandenburg]], [[Germany]]. It consists of a 160-metre [[lattice tower]], which carries a [[Rotor (turbine)|rotor]] 90 metres in diameter. Until two slightly [[Nowy Tomyśl Wind Turbines|taller wind turbines opened]] in Poland in 2012,<ref name="tallest2">{{cite web | url=http://epoznan.pl/news-news-36935-Nowy_Tomysl_powstaly_najwyzsze_wiatraki_na_swiecie | title=Nowy Tomyśl: powstały najwyższe wiatraki na świecie! | language=Polish |publisher=Epoznan | accessdate=4 December 2012 }}</ref> this Fuhrländer was the [[List of tallest buildings and structures in the world|tallest wind turbine in the world]]. Its power output is 2.5 MW.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://fuhrlaender.de/produkte/index_de.php?produkt_gesucht=1&produkt_name=FL+2500 | title=FL 2500 Noch mehr Wirtschaftlichkeit | language=German | publisher=Fuhrlaender AG | accessdate=2009-11-05 }}{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

